"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-30-More-exciting-events-to-follow-on-July-30-at-2024-Paris-Olympics-1vEZZdkGPe0-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Sports Scene  Copied  Tuesday's latest gold medal event schedule will see China's Wang Chuqin and Sun Yingsha taking on the DPRK's Ri Jong Sik and Kim Kum Yong in the table tennis mixed doubles gold medal match at 14:00 (GMT+2), which will be the first gold awarded in the sport at this year's games.  In artistic gymnastics, China's Luo Huan, Ou Yushan, Zhou Yaqin and Qiu Qiyuan will compete in the women's team event at 18:00 (GMT+2).  The women's epee team gold medal match will take place right after the bronze medal contest at 19:30 (GMT+2).  Multiple swimming events will be staged in the evening including the women's 100m backstroke final, men's 800m freestyle final and men's 4x200m freestyle relay final at 20:56 (GMT+2).  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"